{
 "name": "RPlog_Meeting_Adlerson",
 "title": "Meeting Adlerson",
 "summary": "Summoned to an Imperial station, the scarred spacer Morganna is escorted by the smuggler-informant Detjin's departure and met by the menacing Admiral Adlerson, who walks her past prison blocks and weapon scanners to his office. Tense and fearful, Morganna explains how she was boarded, released with conditional trade permits, and pressured into service. Rather than punish her, the coldly civil Adlerson demands only an apology for how she once treated him and asks her to keep her eyes and ears open for information on the rebels and on Director Dixon's Bureau. Morganna, relieved to keep her head, agrees to pass along what she learns, and the two part on guardedly cordial terms.",
